Additional notice for non-code materials
---------------------------------------

The GameGrid name, logo, branding, and any original visual assets, audio,
copywriting, or other game content in this repository are not automatically
licensed for trademark use or commercial brand reuse unless explicitly stated
otherwise in a separate file or notice.

In plain English:
- You can study, modify, and self-host the code under AGPL terms.
- If you run a modified networked version, you must offer the corresponding
  source code to users of that version.
- You do not receive trademark rights to present your fork as official
  GameGrid.
- You should assume original art, branding, and other game-specific content
  are reserved unless a file says otherwise.

This notice is intended to make the repository's licensing intent clear. If a
future commit adds the full verbatim AGPL text, that text will control the
license terms for the code.
